The test steps (per run)
1.	Start remote browser: new RemoteWebDriver(new URL(hubUrl()), browserOptions)
2.	Go to site: driver.get("https://www.saucedemo.com/")
3.	Type username/password, click Login
4.	Assert the page source contains the expected text
5.	On failure, Extent captures a screenshot; after each run the driver quits
How to run (examples)
# Run on Chrome only
mvn -Dbrowser=chrome -Dhub=http://<hub-ip>:4444 test

# Run on both Chrome and Firefox (default)
mvn -Dhub=http://<hub-ip>:4444 test
Report will be at: target/extent/extent.html.
